Area Sales Manager
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 11:28:48
Ref. JB3046276
Job Description
A leading multinational automotive organization is seeking to recruit an Area Sales Manager. The right candidate will be responsible of Sales and Market strategy execution to achieve the regional sales targets. You will also be responsible of the improvement of the quality of operations and focus on customer satisfaction.
The job will require the below responsibilities:
•	Manage the Sales and Marketing activities
•	Develop quality of services and ensure Customers satisfaction
•	Coordinate and effectively communicate with various internal departments
•	Budget development
•	Manage the sales revenues
•	Sales budget allocation to the market
•	Market research/analysis to evaluate the market and set business plan
•	Manage vehicle forecast and orders
•	Implement fleet strategies
Skills
To be considered for this opportunity you must have the following skills and attributes
•	7 to 15 years of experience in the Automotive Industry
•	Good understanding of the regional market
•	Business and Financial Acumen
